# 


arrs=[]

for feature in log_data.keys():
    
    
    # TODOQ125th
    Q1 = np.percentile(log_data[feature],25)
    
    # TODOQ375th
    Q3 = np.percentile(log_data[feature],75)
    
    # TODO1.5
    step = 1.5*(Q3-Q1)
    
    # 
    print "Data points considered outliers for the feature '{}':".format(feature)
    table_Data = log_data[~((log_data[feature] >= Q1 - step) & (log_data[feature] <= Q3 + step))]
    arrs.append(table_Data.index)
    display(table_Data)

index_arrs=[]    
for arr in arrs:
    index_arrs= np.concatenate((index_arrs, arr))

index_num={}    
for first_index in range(len(index_arrs)):
    if(index_num.has_key(index_arrs[first_index])==False):
        index_num[index_arrs[first_index]]=0
        for second_index in range(first_index+1,len(index_arrs)):
            if (index_arrs[first_index]==index_arrs[second_index]):
                index_num[index_arrs[first_index]]+=1
plus_index=[]            
for key in index_num:
    if(index_num[key]>0):
        plus_index.append(key)
print plus_index
